# Aqarify UI Revamp Plan
## Full Frontend Refactor → Recommended Stack

> **Target aesthetic:** Images 1–4 — lime-green accent (`#C8FF00`), cream off-white background, icon-only collapsed sidebar, pill-shaped bar charts, clean property tables, minimal mobile screens.

---

## 0. Audit: Current State vs. Target State

| Area | Current | Target |
|---|---|---|
| Primary color | `#141414` black + `#B8892E` gold | `#C8FF00` lime-green + cream `#F5F2E8` |
| Background | pure white / `#0f0f0f` dark | warm cream `#F5F2E8` |
| Border radius | `0px` sharp luxury | `12–20px` rounded cards, `999px` pill badges |
| Component library | shadcn/ui **+** @heroui/react **+** aceternity (3 conflicting systems) | shadcn/ui **only** (Radix primitives) |
| Charts | none (recharts installed, unused) | Recharts pill-shaped `BarChart` |
| Sidebar | full-width 64px labeled dark sidebar | icon-only collapsed sidebar (light) |
| Shared shell | `SaaSPageShell`, `SaaSKpiCard`, `SaaSListToolbar` | redesigned equivalents |
| Table | basic shadcn Table | TanStack Table + shadcn shell |
| Range slider | none | `@radix-ui/react-slider` |
| Mobile nav | `mobile-bottom-nav.tsx` exists, unstyled | redesigned rounded pill bar |
| Animations | Framer Motion + aceternity effects | Framer Motion only (aceternity removed) |
| Font | Maison Neue / DM Sans | Geist (already in deps) + Cairo (Arabic) |

