## 1. Dependencies

### 1.1 Remove
```bash
# Conflicting / redundant UI libraries
npm uninstall @heroui/react

# Aceternity ships heavy canvas animations not needed
# (files will be deleted manually — no separate npm package)
```

### 1.2 Add
```bash
npm install @tanstack/react-table          # headless data table
npm install @radix-ui/react-slider         # price range slider
npm install vaul                           # drawer (replace current sheet-based drawer)
```

