### 3.2 Update `components/ui/` (shadcn primitives)
Re-run shadcn CLI to regenerate with new radius + color tokens:
```bash
npx shadcn@latest add button card badge input label select \
  checkbox switch slider tabs dialog sheet avatar \
  dropdown-menu popover scroll-area separator skeleton \
