```
No manual edits needed — tokens drive appearance automatically.

### 3.3 Redesign `components/shared/sidebar.tsx`

**Current:** Full-width dark sidebar with text labels.  
**Target:** Icon-only collapsed sidebar (48px wide), icon+label on hover tooltip, dark background, lime active indicator.

```
Sidebar layout:
┌──┐
│🏠│  ← active: left border lime 3px + icon lime
│👤│
│📊│
│⚙️│
└──┘
```

**Key changes:**
- Width: `w-12` (48px) always collapsed on desktop
- Mobile: slide-in sheet (existing pattern, keep)
- Active item: `border-l-[3px] border-lime bg-white/5 text-lime`
- Tooltip on hover via Radix `TooltipProvider` wrapping each `NavLink`
- Remove text labels from desktop view entirely
- Logo area: show favicon/icon only (no full wordmark)

### 3.4 Redesign `components/shared/topbar.tsx`

**Target:** Cream background bar with search icon, notification bell, avatar group cluster (matching Image 1 top-right AI feature area).

Changes:
- Background: `bg-background border-b border-border`
- Add `Monthly` period selector dropdown (shadcn `Select`)
- Add filter/settings icon buttons
- Avatar cluster: use `Avatar` stacked with `-ml-2` for the team cluster shown in Image 1

### 3.5 Redesign `components/shared/saas-kpi-card.tsx`

**Current:** Simple card with title, number, optional icon.  
**Target:** Cards matching Image 1 — large currency number, small subtitle, colored progress bar at bottom.

New props interface:
```tsx
interface KpiCardProps {
  title: string;
  value: string | number;
  subtitle?: string;
  progress?: number;           // 0–100 for bottom bar
  progressColor?: 'lime' | 'striped' | 'default';
  trend?: { value: number; direction: 'up' | 'down' };
}
```

Bottom bar: `lime` = solid lime fill, `striped` = diagonal hatch pattern (CSS `repeating-linear-gradient`), matching exactly Image 1.

### 3.6 New Component: `components/shared/pill-bar-chart.tsx`

Wrapper around Recharts `BarChart` producing the rounded-pill style from Images 1 & 2.

```tsx
