<Bar dataKey="value" radius={[999, 999, 999, 999]} />
// Each bar is a capsule. Selected bar = lime. Others = ink / gray.
```

Props:
```tsx
interface PillBarChartProps {
  data: { day: number; value: number }[];
  activeDay?: number;
  height?: number;
}
```

