## 7. Global Patterns to Enforce (All Pages)

### 7.1 Form pattern
```tsx
// Every form: react-hook-form + zod + shadcn primitives
// No @heroui Form, Input, or Button anywhere
const form = useForm<Schema>({ resolver: zodResolver(schema) });
return (
  <Form {...form}>
    <FormField name="email" render={({ field }) => (
      <FormItem>
        <FormLabel>Email</FormLabel>
        <FormControl><Input {...field} /></FormControl>
        <FormMessage />
      </FormItem>
    )} />
  </Form>
);
```

### 7.2 Dialog / Drawer pattern
```tsx
// Drawers (offer-drawer, filter panels): use vaul <Drawer>
// Modals (confirm delete, create form): use shadcn <Dialog>
// No Sheet for feature-level drawers (Sheet stays for sidebar mobile only)
```

### 7.3 Loading states
```tsx
// Skeleton loading: shadcn <Skeleton> with matching card dimensions
// Page-level: keep existing Suspense + Loader spinner
// Table loading: render skeleton rows with TanStack Table
```

### 7.4 Error states
```tsx
// Inline errors: shadcn <Alert variant="destructive">
// Toast errors: sonner toast.error()
// Page-level: existing RouteErrorBoundary (keep)
```

### 7.5 Empty states
```tsx
// Keep existing empty-state.tsx, update icon + button styles
```

